Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,720)\fs40}希望是个温柔的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,720)\fs40}是啊
